      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now let's get started!</strong></p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> and the <strong>onion wedges</strong> to the pan with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6 min or until the onion is slightly softened</p>",
